      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Legal files, credit books, cash books, vouchers, fund reports, contracts, bids, and many other financial records of the University.</p>
      </scopecontent>
