      <relatedmaterial>
         <head id="a5">RELATED MATERIALS</head>
         <p>Includes collection #7-1-1610, 7-7-1636, 7-1-1345, 7-6-86, 7-6-425, 7-6-13, and 7-6-1110.</p>
         <p>Account books, bond books, mortgage books.</p>
      </relatedmaterial>
      <dsc type="combined">
         <head>CONTAINER LIST</head>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="box">1</container>
               <unittitle>20 Small cash Account Books with First National Bank of Ithaca, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1886 -1911</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="box">1</container>
               <unittitle>1 Small cash Account Book with Fifth Avenue Trust Company, New York City, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1904-1910</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="box">1</container>
               <unittitle>1 Small Journal of Accounts (Investments, Bonds and Stocks) n.d.</unittitle>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">1</container>
               <unittitle>Account book, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1911-1913</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Listing all the expenses of the various departments of the University from <date>May 1911</date> to <date>Mar. 1914</date>. The listings are by departments and identify the appropriation from which each sum was taken.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">2</container>
               <unittitle>Records of Bonds, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1880-1914</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>A listing of university held bonds from <date>Oct. 30, 1880</date> through <date>June 27, 1914</date>. Lists issuing company, type of bond, number issue date, date and place payable, interest payable and principal.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">3</container>
               <unittitle>Records of interest payments on mortgages, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1900-1915</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">4</container>
               <unittitle>Records of mortgages, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1876-1915</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Mortgages book giving complete data on mortgages held by the university from <date>1876</date> to <date>1915</date>. Lists purchase data, mortgagee amount of cash involved, interest rate and date. Also from whom purchased if purchased, and where recorded and where payable.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">5</container>
               <unittitle>Record of interest payments on bonds, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1900-1915</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">6</container>
               <unittitle>Index of Mortgages, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>n.d.</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Index to university mortgage books. No dates. Gives name of mortgage and page number in the entire book.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">7</container>
               <unittitle>Record of Bonds, 
				1880-1931
				; also, Record of mortgages 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1880-1931</unitdate><unitdate>1876-1900</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>List of mortgages financed by the university from <date>Apr. 10, 1876</date> to <date>Jan. 4, 1900</date>. Back of volume contains same listing for bonds from <date>May 8, 1880</date> to <date>Jan. 12, 1900</date>. This book lists complete information on both bonds and mortgages.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">8</container>
               <unittitle>Index (?)</unittitle>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">9</container>
               <unittitle>Index of Mortgages, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>n.d.</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Mortgage and bond book listing the various persons against whom mortgages and bonds were held. It contains an index and all listings are alphabetically arranged along with the folio numbers and amount of cash involved. There are no dates.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">10</container>
               <unittitle>Record of Securities, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1872-1890</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>A listing of the securities in which the university endowment funds were invested. Listed are the purchased date, firm, type of security, number of security, date issued, when payable, amount of interest. </p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">11</container>
               <unittitle>Cash book (outgoing), 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1897-1913</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Day book listing daily payments from <date>Aug. 6, 1899</date> to <date>Feb. 1913</date>. Entries are intermittently placed throughout the book.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">12</container>
               <unittitle>Index of Securities</unittitle>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">13</container>
               <unittitle>C.U. Appropriation book, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1900-1920</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>University appropriations book <date>1900-1920</date>. Lists two years to a page, moneys appropriated for university expenses by department. Lists amount of appropriation, expenditure and balance of appropriation left after each entry.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">14</container>
               <unittitle>C.U. Reports, 
				1864-1868
				(Removed - see Acc. 47-1-1527)</unittitle><unitdate>1864-1868</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">15</container>
               <unittitle>Records of Special Funds, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1879-1885</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>University ledger listing: 1) University land script fund, 2) University endowment, 3) Various university funds. These entries cover the dates, <date>Feb. 1879</date> to <date>June 1885</date> by month and by separate fund.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">16</container>
               <unittitle>General Ledger A, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1868-1871</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Ledger listing the various expenses in an itemized form which the various departments of the university and persons concerned with the university incurred from <date>Nov. 25, 1868</date> to <date>Aug. 31, 1871</date>. Contains an index.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">17</container>
               <unittitle>College of Forestry - Voucher Records, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1899-1914</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Voucher record-College Forest Appropriation Book. Sixty pages of voucher listings by number from 1 to 780. Dates extend from <date>May 20, 1899</date> to <date>Apr. 22, 1914</date>. Each entry describes the person date the sum concerned was appropriated and total of the full appropriation from which the sum was taken.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">18</container>
               <unittitle>College of Forestry - Voucher Record, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1898-1903</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Voucher Record-College Forest Appropriations. Lists date, amount of bill paid and total amount of appropriation from which money was taken. <date>May 12, 1898</date> to <date>Oct. 17, 1903</date>.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">19</container>
               <unittitle>Professional Pension Recod, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1903-1944</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Account book listing professional pension fund payments, by professors name from <date>1903</date> to <date>1947</date>. Index of back cover.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">20</container>
               <unittitle>Student Loan Fund, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1873-1904</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Student Loan Fund book. Students and sums are listed by name from <date>1873-1904</date>.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">21</container>
               <unittitle>Record of Sage College Room Rents, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1895-1900</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Sage College Record of Room Rent <date>1895-1900</date>. Listings are made by person, monthly.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">22</container>
               <unittitle>Abstracts of Ithaca property owned by Ezra Cornell and Cornell University</unittitle>
            </did>
            <scopecontent>
               <p>Seventy-three pages of titles, abstracts, maps and descriptions of various land in and about Ithaca which were transferred through Ezra Cornell to the university. These abstracts have record of land as early as <date>1822</date> and extend up to <date>1867</date>. The various mortgages on the land are also described.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">23</container>
               <unittitle>Account Book (Day Book), 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1886-1871</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">24</container>
               <unittitle>Account Book (Day Book), 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1871-1879</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">25</container>
               <unittitle>Account Book (Day Book), 
				1869-1871
				; Coal Contracts, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1869-1871</unitdate><unitdate>1871-1888</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">26</container>
               <unittitle>Account Book (Day Book), 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1866-1871</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">27</container>
               <unittitle>Account Book (Day Book), 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1870-1871</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">28</container>
               <unittitle>University budget, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1871-1900</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">29</container>
               <unittitle>Agriculture and Home Eco. disbursements, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1926-1927</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">30</container>
               <unittitle>General Ledger D, 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1890-1904</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">31</container>
               <unittitle>Account Book (Cash Book No. 2), 
				</unittitle><unitdate>1882-1891</unitdate>
            </did>
         </c01>
         <c01 level="file">
            <did>
               <container label="unspecified" type="volume">32</container>
